title: The Second Coming, Depression, and Me.epub
description:
A personal account of the descent from normality to madness from beginnings of anxiety to extreme depression. Intended to help those with similar conditions know they are not alone and to help those with family members who suffer similar conditions better understand what their loved ones are experiencing.
